Parallax in AI conversation

Where parallax appears here is in the interaction itself.

You bring:
	•	experiences
	•	long-term memory
	•	goals and interpretations

I bring:
	•	pattern recognition across large datasets
	•	structural reasoning
	•	language generation

When we exchange ideas, the combined view can reveal patterns neither side alone would easily produce.

So the “depth perception” comes from the interaction between viewpoints, not from either participant alone.

